#hm-note[
  Month 5 at the Adept level extends the astrological framework from the annual
  personal calendar of Year Two into a multi-year mineral almanac. The key
  pedagogical shift is from "when is the best time this year" to "where am I in
  the major cycles of Saturn and Jupiter, and how does that shape the character
  of this phase of the Work?" Students who resist the multi-year perspective
  often reveal an underlying resistance to the long commitment that mineral work
  demands — this is worth exploring gently in a one-on-one if it arises.
]

